  <entry>
    <title>About-C++</title>
    <link href="/2022/08/01/About-C/"/>
    <url>/2022/08/01/About-C/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-指针"><a href="#1-指针" class="headerlink" title="1.指针"></a>1.指针</h1><p>指针本身是一个对象，但是它又指向另一个对象，这是指针的两种属性</p><ul><li><p>指针本身是一个常量，指针的指向也是一个常量，也就是说不能改变指针的指向，称其为顶层const(top-level const )</p></li><li><p>顶层const 表示指针本身就是一个常量</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C++"><span class="hljs-type">int</span>* cosnt p1 = &amp;a;<span class="hljs-comment">//p1是顶层const</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​</p></li><li><p>指针指向的对象是一个常量，即指针指向的地址的值是一个常量，不能改变指针指向内存的值，称为底层const(low-level const）</p></li><li><p>底层const表示指针指向的对象是一个常量</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++">cosnt <span class="hljs-type">int</span>* p2 = &amp;a;<span class="hljs-comment">//p2是底层const</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> *<span class="hljs-type">const</span> p1 = &amp;i;       <span class="hljs-comment">// 不能改变p1的值，这是一个顶层const</span><br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> ci = <span class="hljs-number">42</span>;        <span class="hljs-comment">// 不能改变ci的值，这是一个顶层const</span><br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> *p2 = &amp;ci;      <span class="hljs-comment">// 允许改变p2的值，这是一个底层const</span><br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> *<span class="hljs-type">const</span> p3 = p2; <span class="hljs-comment">// 靠右的const是顶层const，靠左的const是底层const</span><br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> &amp;r = ci;        <span class="hljs-comment">// 用于声明引用的const都是底层const</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="指向常量的引用"><a href="#指向常量的引用" class="headerlink" title="指向常量的引用"></a>指向常量的引用</h2><p>程序里有一个<strong>对象r</strong>（C++里对象即变量，可以理解为同义词），现在我想设置一个<strong>【引用】</strong>来<strong>【绑定】</strong>它，但有一个要求：不能<strong>【通过这个引用】</strong>来<strong>【修改】</strong>这个对象的值，但允许通过这个引用来<strong>【读取】</strong>这个对象。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> r = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> &amp;R = r;  <span class="hljs-comment">//引用R绑定了r</span><br>cout &lt;&lt; R;  <span class="hljs-comment">//正确：允许通过引用R读取r的值</span><br>R = <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;      <span class="hljs-comment">//错误：终端提示“ assignment of read-only reference &#x27;R&#x27; ”</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="指向常量的指针"><a href="#指向常量的指针" class="headerlink" title="指向常量的指针"></a>指向常量的指针</h2><p>程序里有一个<strong>对象r</strong>，现在我想设置一个<strong>【指针】</strong>来<strong>【指向】</strong>它，但有一个要求：不能<strong>【通过这个指针】</strong>来<strong>【修改】</strong>这个对象的值，但允许通过这个指针来<strong>【读取】</strong>这个对象。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> r = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> *p = &amp;r;  <span class="hljs-comment">//指针p指向了r</span><br>cout &lt;&lt; *p;  <span class="hljs-comment">//正确：允许通过指针p读取r的值</span><br>*p = <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;      <span class="hljs-comment">//错误：终端提示“ assignment of read-only location &#x27;* p&#x27; ”</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="常量指针"><a href="#常量指针" class="headerlink" title="常量指针"></a>常量指针</h2><p>房子里面的东西可以变，房子的地址不能变</p><p>指向不能变</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> x = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, y = <span class="hljs-number">10</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> *<span class="hljs-type">const</span> p = &amp;x;  <span class="hljs-comment">//指针p指向了x</span><br>*p = <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;     <span class="hljs-comment">//正确：允许通过指针p读取和修改x的值</span><br>p = &amp;y;     <span class="hljs-comment">//错误：终端提示“ assignment of read-only variable &#x27;p&#x27; ”</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="指针和引用的区别"><a href="#指针和引用的区别" class="headerlink" title="指针和引用的区别"></a>指针和引用的区别</h2><ol><li><p>引用不是对象，不分配内存。 指针是对象，分配内存</p><p>引用定义时必须初始化，且只与初始时的对象所绑定，作为该对象的<strong>别名</strong>【而指针本身就是一个<strong>对象</strong>，使用<code>size(引用)</code>得到的是所绑定的对象的类型大小，而<code>sizeof(指针)</code>得到的是这个指针对象本身的类型大小】。</p></li><li><p>引用是类型安全的，而指针不是</p><p>由于必须初始化且与一个对象一直绑定，因此不存在空引用，但指针指向可以随意更改（指针其实也可以理解为一个普通变量，只不过它的变量值是一个地址值，较特别），且允许存在空指针和野指针（野指针可以在多种场景下产生，其中一种情况是当多个指针指向一块内存，free掉一个指针之后，那么别的指针就成为了野指针）。因此引用是类型安全的，而指针不是。类型安全即内存安全。</p></li></ol><h1 id="2-关于const"><a href="#2-关于const" class="headerlink" title="2.关于const"></a>2.关于const</h1><ul><li><p><strong>底层const</strong>:若【通过】<strong>某</strong>【指针&#x2F;引用】<strong>无法对所</strong>【指向&#x2F;绑定】<strong>的对象进行</strong>【值修改】，我们就称该【指针&#x2F;引用】为一个<code>底层const</code></p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> m = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> &amp;M = m;         <span class="hljs-comment">//错误：普通的int&amp;不能绑定到int整型常量上（反证法：如果可以，那通过M就能修改m的值，这样就和m是常量的规定发生冲突）</span><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> r = <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> &amp;R = r;   <span class="hljs-comment">//这就是上面的例子。等号右侧的表达式`r`其类型是`int整型`，可以转换成int整型常量`，因此不会报错</span><br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> &amp;x = <span class="hljs-number">10</span>;  <span class="hljs-comment">//等号右侧的表达式`10`其类型为`整型字面值常量`，可以转换成`int整型常量`</span><br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> &amp;y = r*<span class="hljs-number">2</span>+<span class="hljs-number">3</span>;  <span class="hljs-comment">//等号右侧表达式的计算结果同样为`整型字面值常量`</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​</p></li><li><p><strong>顶层const</strong>:若对象<strong>【自身是一个常量】</strong>，不可变，则自身就是<code>顶层const</code></p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> x = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;  <span class="hljs-comment">//x就是一个顶层const</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h1 id="关于NULL和nullptr"><a href="#关于NULL和nullptr" class="headerlink" title="关于NULL和nullptr"></a>关于NULL和nullptr</h1>  <figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">Func_serven</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">void</span>* serven_void)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;I am void fucntion!&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">Func_serven</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> serven_zero)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;I am zero fucntion!&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">Func_serven</span>(<span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">Func_serven</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>  <figure class="highlight mathematica"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs mathematica">执行结果如下 <br><span class="hljs-built_in">I</span> <span class="hljs-variable">am</span> <span class="hljs-variable">zero</span> <span class="hljs-variable">fucntion</span><span class="hljs-operator">!</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">I</span> <span class="hljs-variable">am</span> <span class="hljs-variable">zero</span> <span class="hljs-variable">fucntion</span><span class="hljs-operator">!</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">E</span><span class="hljs-operator">:</span>\<span class="hljs-variable">c</span><span class="hljs-operator">++</span>\<span class="hljs-variable">code</span>\<span class="hljs-operator">.</span><span class="hljs-variable">vscode</span>\<span class="hljs-built_in">C</span><span class="hljs-operator">++</span><span class="hljs-number">3</span>\<span class="hljs-variable">x64</span>\<span class="hljs-built_in">Debug</span>\<span class="hljs-variable">test</span> <span class="hljs-variable">NULL</span> 和<span class="hljs-variable">nullptr</span><span class="hljs-operator">.</span><span class="hljs-variable">exe</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">(</span>进程 <span class="hljs-number">29168</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">)</span>已退出，代码为 <span class="hljs-number">0</span>。<br>按任意键关闭此窗口<span class="hljs-operator">.</span> <span class="hljs-operator">.</span> <span class="hljs-operator">.</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>  <figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">Func_serven</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">void</span>* serven_void)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;I am void fucntion!&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">Func_serven</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> serven_zero)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;I am zero fucntion!&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">Func_serven</span>((<span class="hljs-type">void</span>*)<span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>);<span class="hljs-comment">// 强制转为空指针</span><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">Func_serven</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>  <figure class="highlight mathematica"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs mathematica"><span class="hljs-built_in">I</span> <span class="hljs-variable">am</span> <span class="hljs-variable">void</span> <span class="hljs-variable">fucntion</span><span class="hljs-operator">!</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">I</span> <span class="hljs-variable">am</span> <span class="hljs-variable">zero</span> <span class="hljs-variable">fucntion</span><span class="hljs-operator">!</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">E</span><span class="hljs-operator">:</span>\<span class="hljs-variable">c</span><span class="hljs-operator">++</span>\<span class="hljs-variable">code</span>\<span class="hljs-operator">.</span><span class="hljs-variable">vscode</span>\<span class="hljs-built_in">C</span><span class="hljs-operator">++</span><span class="hljs-number">3</span>\<span class="hljs-variable">x64</span>\<span class="hljs-built_in">Debug</span>\<span class="hljs-variable">test</span> <span class="hljs-variable">NULL</span> 和<span class="hljs-variable">nullptr</span><span class="hljs-operator">.</span><span class="hljs-variable">exe</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">(</span>进程 <span class="hljs-number">21936</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">)</span>已退出，代码为 <span class="hljs-number">0</span>。<br>按任意键关闭此窗口<span class="hljs-operator">.</span> <span class="hljs-operator">.</span> <span class="hljs-operator">.</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  查看源码中的NULL 定义如下：</p><p>  发现NULL有二义性，即可表示 int 0 又可以表示 （void*） 0</p>  <figure class="highlight lua"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs lua">#ifndef NULL<br>    #ifdef __cplusplus<br>        #define NULL <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br>    #<span class="hljs-keyword">else</span><br>        #define NULL ((void *)<span class="hljs-number">0</span>)<br>    #endif<br>#endif<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  于是 C++11标准中引入了一个新的关键字nullptr</p><p>  nullptr是nullptr_t类型的右值常量，专门用于初始化空指针</p>  <figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-type">nullptr_t</span> ser_ptr;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span>* serven_1 = ser_str;      <span class="hljs-comment">// 定义一个整型指针，指向空</span><br><br>  <span class="hljs-type">int</span>* serven_3 = <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>;<br>  <span class="hljs-type">char</span>* serven_4 = <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>;<br>  <span class="hljs-type">double</span>* serven_5 = <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>;<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  <strong>总结 使用nullptr可以使得我们的程序更加健壮</strong></p><h1 id="基于范围的for循环"><a href="#基于范围的for循环" class="headerlink" title="基于范围的for循环"></a>基于范围的for循环</h1><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (declaration : expression)&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">//循环体</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​    </p><ul><li>declaration：表示此处要定义一个变量，该变量的类型为要遍历序列中存储元素的类型。需要注意的是，C++ 11 标准中，declaration参数处定义的变量类型可以用 auto 关键字表示，该关键字可以使编译器自行推导该变量的数据类型。</li><li>expression：表示要遍历的序列，常见的可以为事先定义好的普通数组或者容器，还可以是用 {} 大括号初始化的序列。</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    
